				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Haste songs stacking...<a name="2911"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jan 9 03 10:53 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Also remember that there are 3 kinds of Bard song haste that stack. If you take at lucy.fnord.net you will see 3 things:
<br />

<br />
1. Increase Attack Speed by X% (L57) to X%. This is normal haste. V1 haste per se. The higher of this haste for any song will be taken. Enchanter haste will override tihs
<br />

<br />
2. Increase Haste v2 by X%. Ervaj series. Will stack with any V1 or V3 haste
<br />

<br />
3. Increase Haste v3 by X%. Battlecry/Warsong series. Will stack with any V1 or V2 haste.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
